  "description": "Normalization is dividing a quantity by a base to make it comparable. Raw numbers are hard to compare — a site earning $500 from 100,000 pageviews and a site earning $50 from 1,000 pageviews look different until you normalize by pageviews: $5 RPM vs $50 RPM.",
